  "subject": "Remove extra \"synchronized\" on update publisher",
  "commit_message": "Remove extra \"synchronized\" on update publisher\n\nSeeing a possible deadlock in xacml-pdp since adding \"synchronized\" to a\nnumber of methods.  Most of them do not look like they'd cause a\ndeadlock.  However, the one that was added to the update publisher is a\nbit more questionable, thus removed it.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-3531\nChange-Id: I1f7d8117be11987f2db69bfea73206513b432501\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\n",
